com.sun.identity.authentication.share

Interface AuthenticationCallbackXMLHelper


  • public interface AuthenticationCallbackXMLHelper
    Defines the interface that allows Authentication service to implement the XML processing of required Authentication Callback during Authentication remote SDK execution. The implementation of this interface is determined during runtime.
    See Also:
    AuthenticationCallbackXMLHelperFactory
